<h2>2 · Why <code>velocity_y &gt; 0</code>? 🤔</h2>
<p>The player can touch a platform while moving up <em>or</em> down. We only want to land when moving <strong>down</strong>.</p>
<p><strong>What would go wrong if we removed the <code>velocity_y &gt; 0</code> check and the player jumped up through a platform?</strong></p>
